{"tid":2495394,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來雲加十年前已經預言有歐超聯","createTime":"2021-04-19T07:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:42:30.000Z","uid":135753,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6a504a0c5171ee533c6d40877f76ff42e51a4c","tid":2495394,"uid":135753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:10:30.000Z","msg":"最近，雲加接受了《衛報》的採訪，並談到了他對歐洲超級聯賽的看法。 這位法國人目前與歐洲足聯超級聯賽沒有任何聯繫。 在2009年，他做出了歐洲聯盟超級聯賽即將誕生的預測。<br />\n<br />\n 雲加當時相信，十年之內，歐洲超級聯賽的想法可能會成為現實。 他感到有些歐洲領先的俱樂部不再對冠軍聯賽的收穫感到滿意。<br />\n<br />\n今天早些時候，有12家領先的歐洲俱樂部建立了一個新的賽事，即歐洲超級聯賽。 本次活動將由贊助俱樂部管理。 這12個俱樂部是皇馬，巴塞羅那，馬德里體育會，AC米蘭，國際米蘭，祖雲達斯，曼聯，曼城，利物浦，阿仙奴，車路士和熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e615f7cbf36cb9044054493eac148bb914a545","tid":2495394,"uid":135753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcd7d7ff993550dec032a32d14a5a2831dec457","tid":2495394,"uid":153976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66bf8960a07f077c15301daf7892f642db77181","tid":2495394,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"我懷疑跟本雲格就係幕後搞手"},{"pid":"2eb25118c3c7564d4177acd7d75447c31ad438c2","tid":2495394,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:20:01.000Z","msg":"爺爺不嬲睇開10~20年之後既環境，反雲黨悔改未？"},{"pid":"90d30a47dd83fb961e48ce804731053d5dcfef8f","tid":2495394,"uid":7609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"幕後搞手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e460af3b2169c5002dd94c9d8a8793793740d9","tid":2495394,"uid":3503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021